author: Keith Sargeant | NJ Advance Media for NJ.com
title: How did White Sox star Todd Frazier troll Miami baseball alums following Rutgers' win?
text: Todd Frazier enters his seventh Major League Baseball season for the Chicago White Sox but couldn't help call out Ryan Braun, Yonder Alonso, Jon Jay and other Miami alums following the Rutgers baseball team's upset win on Sunday.
